title: Car rental in the U.S. - total cars in service 2002 to 2012
summary: Overall Cars in service in thousands has decreased over the Year.
Cars in service in thousands is slightly increasing from 2005 to 2006, roughly constant from 2006 to 2008, and finally slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2009.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Cars in service in thousands, about 1861.0 was reported at Year 2007
Minimum Cars in service in thousands about 1637.0 was reached at Year 2009
